WEBVTT

00:00:00.171 --> 00:00:03.800
Because you are leading global enterprises, you face a unique challenge.

00:00:04.261 --> 00:00:08.451
The mechanics of trust and communication change drastically across borders.

00:00:09.092 --> 00:00:13.102
A global mindset allows you to understand the interdependence of the global economy.

00:00:13.603 --> 00:00:19.958
But cultural intelligence focuses on the behavioral ability to interact interpersonally and bridge cultural differences.
